==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unionist
<hw>Un"ion*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who advocates or
promotes union; especially a loyal supporter of a federal union, as that
of the United States.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A member or supporter of a trades union.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unionistic</ent>⟦br⟧
